      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="related">
      <div class="related-inner">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">Related</p>
        <h2 class="section-headline">Keep going.</h2>
        <div class="related-grid">
          <a href="/learn/smelly-feet-spray/" class="related-card">
            <h3>Smelly feet spray</h3>
            <p>The routine that treats the feet and the footwear together — and holds.</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/learn/foot-deodorant-vs-powder-vs-spray/" class="related-card">
            <h3>Powder vs. soak vs. spray</h3>
